Clicking back inside the folder or long clicking on it
Could not find git in this directory

Action.label: Enable permission 'Run commands in Termux environment'
bash /sdcard/tg_config.sh
Action.Str:
d="$HOME/.termux" f="$d/termux.properties"
if [ ! -d "$d" ]; then mkdir "$d" fi
permission="\n\nallow-external-apps=true\n"
if ! grep -qs allow-external-apps "$f"; then echo -e $permission >> "$f" fi
if ! [ -x "$(command -v git)" ]; then pkg update && pkg upgrade pkg install git openssh fi

org="%evtprm(1)" dst="%dir/git/%name/"
if [ ! -d "$dst" ]; then mkdir "$dst" git init "$dst"
git config --global user.name "%user" git config --global user.email "%email" fi
cd "$dst"
cp "$org" . git add . git commit -m "%input"
Please add your username and email in 'GT - .Config User'

git config --global user.name "%user" git config --global user.email "%email" fi
cd "$dst"

status="$(git status | grep ' ' | sed 's/\t//g')" git commit -m "$status"

git remote add origin '%input' b="$(git branch -l | grep '^* ' | sed 's/^* //g')" git push -u origin "$b"

stout="$(cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub)" am broadcast -a SSH -e stout "$stout"
